These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, baccarat, montecristo, chaman, bluemaster
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, taxi, subway, car, bike
There are 5 different nationalities: british, chinese, egyptian, malaysian, turkish
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, november, march, february, april
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the montecristo-smoker is the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the train##1
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 7. the british is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 9. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
10. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the bluemaster-smoker is between the chinese and the person driving the bike##2
12. the malaysian is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
13. the turkish is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Cigar      | tiparillo        | baccarat | bluemaster     | montecristo   | chaman |
| Transport   | subway     | taxi      | car | bike   | train    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | chinese     | british | egyptian | turkish  |
| Birthday           | november | march      | april     | february   | august     |

