.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: musical, western, crime, horror, animation
The people have 5 different jobs:  firefighter, doctor, bartender, dancer, engineer
5 different pets are kept: ferret, cat, mouse, snake, bird
 1. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
 2. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the doctor##1
 5. the owner of the cat is between the firefighter and the person watching animation movies##2
 6. the owner of the snake is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the bartender is the person watching horror movies##1
 9. the bartender is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
11. the bartender is the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the owner of the cat is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | gardening | writing    | hiking  | reading    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation    | western       | crime      | musical | horror        |
| Job   | engineer   | doctor     | firefighter    | dancer  | bartender     |
| Pet     | mouse    | cat | bird | snake | ferret |

