.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, taxi, van, train
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, apricot, black, chestnut, green
City: edinburgh, hamburg, miami, liverpool, san-francisco
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who likes apricot##1
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes chestnut is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 7. the person who likes green is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the person who likes black is on the far left##1
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person driving the van##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who likes green##1
13. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person driving the train and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Transport   | train  | jet-ski | car | van | taxi        |
| Color   | black      | apricot      | chestnut       | green       | lavender       |
| City         | hamburg | san-francisco  | liverpool    | edinburgh    | miami        |

