.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, goldfish, snake, rat, pony
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, roller, ship, snowmobile, helicopter
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, indie, reggae, rock
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, western, sports, documentary
 1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is between the fan of reggae and the owner of the rat##2
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
10. the fan of reggae is the person watching disaster movies##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
12. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1
13. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Pet          | pony  | snake     | rat   | goldfish     | rabbit |
| Transport         | helicopter | train    | ship  | snowmobile | roller   |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | dubstep    | rock     | indie     | reggae    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | western | sports | documentary | disaster   |

