The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, daffodil, amaryllis, poppy, zinnia
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, ship, roller, tram, bike
 1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person driving the ship and the havana-smoker##2
 5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 8. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
11. the havana-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
12. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
13. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | milk       | mirinda       | almond-milk   | lemonade      | juice    |
| Cigar       | vegafina | bluemaster        | havana       | bongani       | montecristo |
