.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
5 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, pony, goat, rat
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, reading, traveling, video-games
The people have 5 different jobs:  fisherman, engineer, teacher, freelancer, police-officer
House: craftsman, victorian, ranch-style, cottage, wooden
 1. the police-officer is between the victorian house and the engineer##2
 2. the teacher is on the left of the freelancer##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the police-officer##1
 5. the victorian house is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the victorian house##1
 7. the craftsman house is on the right of the wooden house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the teacher is on the far left##1
11. the ranch-style house is between the teacher and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Pet    | pony       | goat    | rat | hedgehog  | dog        |
| Hobby       | video-games | card-games | reading  | traveling | drawing    |
| Job       | teacher        | freelancer   | engineer  | police-officer   | fisherman |
| House   | cottage       | ranch-style      | wooden      | craftsman | victorian  |

