.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
5 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, whist, chess, canasta
5 different pets are kept: lizard, turtle, dog, guinea-pig, frog
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, begonia, rose, aconite, orchid
 1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person watching crime movies and the owner of the dog##2
 3. the person playing chess is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person playing chess is between the owner of the frog and the person who growsbegonia##2
 7. the person who growsaconite is the person playing whist##1
 8. the person playing snooker is the person who growsrose##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
10. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the owner of the dog is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Game      | snooker      | backgammon         | chess      | whist | canasta     |
| Pet           | turtle | dog | guinea-pig | frog    | lizard  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| Flower   | rose  | begonia        | amaryllis   | aconite    | orchid     |

