.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
House: colonial, palace, farmhouse, ranch-style, victorian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, bluemaster, ritmeester, davidoff, blend
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, daisy, balloon-flower, marigold, sunflower
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 3. the victorian house is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growsdaisy is between the bolivar-smoker and the person who growsaconite##2
 6. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the farmhouse house is between the person driving the airplane and the victorian house##2
 8. the palace house is between the ranch-style house and the colonial house##2
 9. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the colonial house##1
10. the colonial house is on the right of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| House         | victorian  | farmhouse | ranch-style   | palace      | colonial |
| Cigar   | bolivar   | davidoff    | bluemaster | blend | ritmeester      |
| Flower           | balloon-flower | daisy    | aconite       | marigold     | sunflower      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

