.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, may, january, boston-climbing, september
5 different games are played: chess, monopoly, canasta, whist, backgammon
City: san-francisco, colone, berlin, london, boston
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is between the malaysian and the person traveling to boston##2
 3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the thai and the person traveling to berlin##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the person playing canasta is the person traveling to london##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in boston-climbing is the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the american is the person traveling to colone##1
10. the person who's birthday is in boston-climbing is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
12. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Birthday         | january    | september  | may  | october      | boston-climbing |
| Game   | monopoly    | backgammon   | whist | canasta | chess   |
| City   | berlin | san-francisco    | boston    | london       | colone         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 